{"tid":107061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭口號性用品撞名　造勢甩拖","createTime":"2017-02-04T07:40:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-04T09:10:08.000Z","uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9eff5784102e87697be533f72d27d6656cd6046f","tid":107061,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T07:40:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170203/bkn-20170203205441045-0203_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170203%2Fbkn-20170203205441045-0203_00822_001.html&d=01EY%2BZdPKRb21p6QCrTOV7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=f437a4eb\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170203/bkn-20170203205441045-0203_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n特首選舉參選人、前政務司司長林鄭月娥尋日舉行造勢大會，正式公布「同行We Connect」嘅競選口號，但隨即被網民發現口號同一款情趣手機應用程式（App）「We-Connect」相同，呢個App能夠遙距操控震動自慰器，真係出師不利。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭喺造勢大會上解釋，選擇此口號係因為近年社會出現撕裂，缺少和諧，社會停滯不前，希望能再次團結，同行向前，所以包括佢在內嘅競選團隊都着上印有「We Connect」嘅藍色競選T恤。<br />\n<br />\n不過口號曝光後引起網民熱烈討論，事關We-Connect係一個情趣App，情侶可透過手機遙控操作震動自慰器，此App仲有聊天、語音及視頻功能，可以透過屏幕控制自慰器震動或強度，故情侶即使分隔兩地亦可享魚水之歡。<br />\n<br />\n除此之外，林鄭尋日喺一班年輕人陪同下進場時，右腳隻鞋不慎飛脫，要急急着番，未開波就甩鞋，認真「甩轆」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170203/photo/bkn-20170203205441045-0203_00822_001_01b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170203%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170203205441045-0203_00822_001_01b.jpg&h=ec301ffc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cdd124c27430f1334cae312b7a44d349f7be9df","tid":107061,"uid":59695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T08:28:59.000Z","msg":"收咁廣告贊助？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7433067a23a34f95197c02e026af3cbd2986bcbc","tid":107061,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T08:34:52.000Z","msg":"佢做乜成日製作笑話"},{"pid":"ebf4686063644bdc788f13dd9afc79b5af1da423","tid":107061,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T08:45:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://we-vibe.com/app\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwe-vibe.com%2Fapp&d=01EY%2BZdPKRb21p6QCrTOV7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=093bc058\" target=\"_blank\">http://we-vibe.com/app</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63f9e2793d8cadc0443acf997ec50caa87f834e6","tid":107061,"uid":32706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T08:50:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/8ahw02c5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F8ahw02c5&h=e1f27a2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前後都插埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e2890c440c2d62a6b7717b28ceb8c363170bef3","tid":107061,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T09:10:08.000Z","msg":"情趣用品公司，要唔要申報選舉經費？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}